<p><span class="anchor" id="p23"></span><span class="c2">( ... - ٣٣١ هـ)</span> <span class="c2">( ... - ٩٤٣ م)</span> يعقوب بن عبد الرحمن الحصاص <span class="c2">(٢)</span><a href="#p23" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
